description:
Adron Buske is the writer of the “Vital Signs” comics anthology, co-creator of steampunk-fantasy series “Amby Verce & The Ascenders”, and creator of the upcoming “Sorceroid” and “Mnemosyren” books.

His previous comic releases include the fantasy adventure “Good Intentions”, and supernatural buddy comedy “Loop & Hoodie”.

Adron and his wife, Wendy Buske, are the co-creators of Nerd for a Living, a resource website and marketing service dedicated to helping nerds discover fulfilling career paths in fandom-related industries. They host an interview podcast at NerdForALiving.com.
